cdata.name: CryptoInsight
cdata.desc:
CryptoInsightis initially a mobile application that will leverage the Ethereum blockchain to implement a fully fledged web platform.Trackraims to provide a real-time alert on cryptocurrency market shifts and an interface to view and manage the portfolio. In addition,Trackrwill also use historical data models and apply machine learning to obtain prediction models.

Trackrtoken in an ERC-20 token, that will be used as a subscription fee to access certain features of the platform.
